workhorse-agent / internal/tools/builtin/gitignore
====================================================

This package is a vendored copy of three source files from go-git, used here
to provide .gitignore pattern matching for the Grep tool without pulling
the full go-git module into go.mod.

Upstream source
---------------
Repository : https://github.com/go-git/go-git
Tag        : v5.19.1
Commit SHA : 3c3be601aa6c
Path       : plumbing/format/gitignore
Retrieved  : 2026-05-26

Files included
--------------
- pattern.go   (verbatim, no modifications)
- matcher.go   (verbatim, no modifications)
- doc.go       (verbatim, no modifications)
- LICENSE      (Apache-2.0, from go-git repository root)

Files NOT included
------------------
- dir.go / dir_test.go: depend on go-billy filesystem abstraction; not needed
  here because workhorse-agent has its own walker (internal/tools/builtin).
- pattern_test.go / matcher_test.go: upstream tests use the gopkg.in/check.v1
  framework, which would re-introduce a transitive dependency. Equivalent
  coverage is provided by tests in this directory written against the standard
  library `testing` package.

Modifications
-------------
None to vendored files. If we ever need to patch, record the change here.

